  "texts": [
    "These words are indicative of the prevalent themes and issues within specific event types.",
    "Understanding the context and relationships between these prevalent informative words and specific event types can potentially provide valuable insights into the factors contributing to different types of PSEs.",
    "Furthermore, we have evaluated the top-performing ML classifier's performance on 2 subsets of PSE reports, differentiated by whether the highlighted word by LIME is relevant to the predicted event type.",
    "Our findings reveal that the majority of PSE reports (93/126) have at least 1 relevant word highlighted, with the classifier achieving an accuracy of 84% (78/93) on these reports.",
    "Conversely, accuracy drops to 52% (17/33) when irrelevant words are highlighted."
